OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1774976748
OL,3,CDelivery driver jailed for killing dog
OL,4,Cwalker in hit-and-run
OL,6,FA judge has told a takeaway driver he
OL,7,Fwas more concerned "with saving his
OL,8,Fown skin" than helping a man he had
OL,9,Fjust hit and killed with his car.
OL,11,F28-year-old Daniel Wyke from
OL,12,FCarmarthen was sentenced to four-and-a-
OL,13,Fhalf years in prison for causing the
OL,14,Fdeath of Aaron Jones, in the village
OL,15,Fof Llanpumsaint, as he walked the
OL,16,Ffamily dog on 23 December, 2024.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
