OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,497,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1774976748
OL,3,CDelivery driver jailed for killing dog
OL,4,Cwalker in hit-and-run
OL,6,FWyke left the scene to continue his
OL,7,Fdelivery job while neighbours found 38-
OL,8,Fyear-old Mr Jones' body partially
OL,9,Fsubmerged in a churchyard pond, after
OL,10,Fdiscovering his dog roaming the
OL,11,Fvillage.
OL,13,FThe court heard Mr Jones was propelled
OL,14,Fover a churchyard wall after being hit
OL,15,Fby Wykes' speeding vehicle. The impact
OL,16,Fcaused a 'bullseye' type crack to the
OL,17,Fwindscreen, consistent with a car
OL,18,Fhitting a pedestrian.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,497,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1774976748
OL,3,CDelivery driver jailed for killing dog
OL,4,Cwalker in hit-and-run
OL,6,FWitnesses saw Wyke leave his vehicle
OL,7,Fand look over the churchyard wall
OL,8,Fbefore fleeing the scene in his
OL,9,Fheavily damaged car.
OL,11,FDuring the sentencing, the court was
OL,12,Ftold Mr Jones had been wearing a high-
OL,13,Fvisibility jacket the night of the
OL,14,Fcollision and was hit on a road with a
OL,15,F20mph speed limit with street lighting
OL,16,Fmeters away.
OL,18,FInvestigators found there was no
OL,19,Fevidence of Wyke attempting to brake
OL,20,Fheavily or steer before the collision.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,497,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1774976748
OL,3,CDelivery driver jailed for killing dog
OL,4,Cwalker in hit-and-run
OL,6,FMr Jones died as a result of a blunt
OL,7,Fhead injury to the back of his head.
OL,8,FHis mother, Maria Steadman, told the
OL,9,Fcourt her son was "a gentle and loving
OL,10,Fsoul" and that her family "now face a
OL,11,Flife sentence", after her only son was
OL,12,Ftaken away from her.
OL,14,FDaniel Wyke told police officers
OL,15,Fduring his arrest that he was unaware
OL,16,Fhe had hit anyone and believed he had
OL,17,Fcollided with a tree branch. However
OL,18,Fhe pleaded guilty to causing death by
OL,19,Fdangerous driving at a court hearing
OL,20,Flast month.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,497,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1774976748
OL,3,CDelivery driver jailed for killing dog
OL,4,Cwalker in hit-and-run
OL,6,FSentencing Wyke, Judge Paul Thomas KC
OL,7,Fsaid: "When you drove down that
OL,8,Fcountry road at 14mph over the speed
OL,9,Flimit, you failed to see a man who was
OL,10,Fwearing a high-visibility jacket and
OL,11,Fwalking his dog.
OL,13,F"You should have seen him for several
OL,14,Fseconds before you hit him. You should
OL,15,Fhave seen him for a hundred meters or
OL,16,Fmore, to put that into context, it's
OL,17,Fthe length of a rugby pitch.
OL,19,F"You clearly weren't looking down the
OL,20,Froad, or you would have seen him for a
OL,21,Fconsiderable distance.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,497,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1774976748
OL,3,CDelivery driver jailed for killing dog
OL,4,Cwalker in hit-and-run
OL,6,F"After you hit Mr Jones with your car
OL,7,Fat 34mph, it must have been obvious to
OL,8,Fyou that you had hit someone and
OL,9,Fcaused them serious injury.
OL,11,F"The presence of the dog and your
OL,12,Fdecision to look over the wall leads
OL,13,Fme to the conclusion that you
OL,14,Fprioritised avoiding the consequences
OL,15,Fof what you had done rather than
OL,16,Ftrying to give him any help or call
OL,17,Ffor help.
OL,19,F"That, in my view, was cruelly
OL,20,Finhumane.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,497,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1774976748
OL,3,CDelivery driver jailed for killing dog
OL,4,Cwalker in hit-and-run
OL,6,F"It will never be known whether timely
OL,7,Fintervention would have saved Aaron
OL,8,FJones' life, but you didn't even take
OL,9,Fthat chance as you were more concerned
OL,10,Fwith saving your own skin.
OL,12,F"You decided to drive off, continued
OL,13,Fyour rounds, and swapped to your
OL,14,Ffather's car.
OL,16,F"You have persistently lied over many
OL,17,Fmonths about knowing that you had hit
OL,18,FMr Jones. You maintained a false and
OL,19,Ffrankly ludicrous story that you had
OL,20,Fhit a tree branch or something similar.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,497,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1774976748
OL,3,CDelivery driver jailed for killing dog
OL,4,Cwalker in hit-and-run
OL,6,F"I have to say, I believe there is a
OL,7,Fstrong element of self-pity rather
OL,8,Fthan true remorse.
OL,10,F"Your dangerous driving cost the life
OL,11,Fof a well-loved father, adored husband
OL,12,Fand son and dear friend to many; his
OL,13,Floss can not be put right by anything
OL,14,Fthis court does."
OL,16,FDaniel Wyke was also disqualified from
OL,17,Fdriving for eight years.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@QO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/9
